From ya boys HONDO and TAN, Thank you to ALL the HOMIES, FANS, n BABY GIRLS for riding with us!!! Get ready for one hell of a send off SEASON 7!!!! Let’s GO!!!!! 👊🏽👊🏼🔥🔥

Live to fight another day. The resilience of this show and our fans was on full display this past weekend. Getting cancelled on Friday and un-cancelled on Monday brought a whirlwind of emotions for all of us, as we’ve poured our hearts and souls into #SWAT for six amazing seasons. Even after the news of cancellation, it didn’t feel like it was over just yet. 

Thank you @sptv @cbstv and the entire @swatcbs fam for letting us give the show and our characters a proper send-off. And shout out to our fearless leader @shemarfmoore for always fighting for what’s right. 

SWAT. SEASON 7. THE LAST DANCE. LET’S GO!!! 🖐🏽✌🏽💥

Leaving my 30s behind. 

Thank you everyone for the birthday wishes. I can feel all the love, and am sending it right back! 

It was an epic decade, with so many memories, and so many milestones. 

Do what makes you happy, with the people who inspire you and make you happiest. 

Dream the biggest dreams, and go after them with relentless drive and determination. You’ll have fewer regrets, no matter what the outcome.

And lastly, see as much of the world as you can. 

Cheers to making the most of the next 10.
